channel.title: *Error when running run.bat after changing server names*
channel.description:
hi guys i just downloaded alhassa-scape from the forums and changed all of the alhassa-scape names to my server name. now when i try to run the server i get this error[img]http://i1231.photobucket.com/albums/ee519/rangekid15/Capture-1.png[/img]
help would be greatly appreciated so i can get my server up and running
p.s. the server was running fine before i changed the names

item.title: *Error when running run.bat after changing server names*
item.dc:creator: @ExtremeX-Scape Ryley
item.description:
@ExtremeX-Scape wrote:

You have a older version of JDK than the server was compiled with. Recompile.
